Google Patches 34 Browser Bugs in Chrome 67, Adds Spectre Fixes
Google has rolled out its newest browser version (Chrome 67.0.3396.62) for Windows, Mac and Linux this week with new Spectre patch, biometric features, improved VR and added support for the credential management API called WebAuthn
https://threatpost.com/google-patches-34-browser-bugs-in-chrome-67-adds-spectre-fixes/132370/

